					"body": "{html}<div><p>Its not really a hack, its adding a device family (iPad) to the\nbuilder.py file. If you go to HD/Library/Application\nSupport/Titanium/mobilesdk/osx/the_build_you_are_using/iphone/builder.py\nline 682 and TARGETED_DEVICE_FAMILY=1 to TARGETED_DEVICE_FAMILY=1,2\nand that will work.</p></div>{html}",
