					"body": "{html}<div><p>(from <a href=\n\"/projects/32238/changesets/61fbf1550144115ed21cdaf69c37d24d85d1afbb\"\ntitle=\n\"Changeset [61fbf1550144115ed21cdaf69c37d24d85d1afbb]\">[61fbf1550144115ed21cdaf69c37d24d85d1afbb]</a>)\n[<a href=\"/projects/32238/tickets/1041\" title=\n\"Ticket #1041\">#1041</a> state:fixed-in-qa] Addition of universal\nbinary support to build scripts. <a href=\n\"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/61fbf1550144115ed21cdaf69c37d24d85d1afbb\">\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/61fbf1550144...</a></p></div>{html}",
